" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Levels of prevention",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 370px; height: 176px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Primary prevention prevents disease from occurring. Secondary prevention detects and cures disease in the asymptomatic phase. Tertiary prevention reduces complications of disease.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
