"     Reproduced with permission from: Fletcher RF, Fletcher SW. Prevention. In: Clinical Epidemiology - The Essentials, 4th ed. Lippincott Williams &amp; Wilkins, Baltimore, 2005. Copyright &copy; 2005 Lippincott Williams and Wilkins.",
